	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001009_0001"/><!--pb/@n='20r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>57 Sloane St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">28<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> April 
<lb/>1857</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p>You will oblige 
<lb/>me if you let my 
<lb/>African &amp; English 
<lb/>friend <persName>Major 
<lb/>Vardon</persName> have a 
<lb/>peep at the Falls<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>He is a good 
<lb/>judge of lions 
<lb/>and if you have 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001009_0002"/><!--pb/@n='20v'--> 
<lb/>the lion &amp; myself by 
<lb/>you I should like 
<lb/>if you could 
<lb/>shew him that 
<lb/>too. I have got 
<lb/>no slips lately</p>
<lb/><p>I am &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p><persName>D. Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I would like him 
<lb/>to see any of 
<lb/>the animals you 
<lb/>have by you 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001009_0003"/><!--pb/@n='21r'--> 
<lb/>as he is a good 
<lb/>judge of what 
<lb/>they ought to be<reg>.</reg></p>
			
</div>
